 1 portion","2294 kJ \/ 546 kcal","22 g","41 g","31 g"],"hintsAndTricks":["Leftover starter will last in the refrigerator in a sealed jar for 2-3 days and can be used to make a 2nd batch of soup.","Serve soup with crusty bread on the side."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","96h 30m","4 portions"]}